---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Home"
  description="Welcome to Graphics Programming Virtual Meetup, a weekly virtual meetup dedicated to graphics programming!"
>
  <h1>Graphics Programming Virtual Meetup</h1>

  <p>
    Welcome, Computer Graphics lovers! We are a virtual meetup dedicated to
    graphics programming.
  </p>
  <p>Since 2020, we have hosted hundreds of meetings almost every week.</p>
  <p>
    We usually work through computer graphics books or articles on a weekly
    basis, though sometimes we have project presentations from members.
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>
      Join our weekly
      <a href="https://www.meetup.com/graphics-programming-virtual-meetup">
        meetings
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>Join our <a href="https://discord.gg/TsTDb4uYfR">Discord group</a></li>
    <li>
      See our
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbX05PBAE-582PYaRXdjRnw">
        Youtube channel
      </a>
      for past video recording
    </li>
    <li>
      Follow us on
      <a href="https://mastodon.gamedev.place/@graphicsmeetup" rel="me">
        Mastodon
      </a>
      and
      <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/gpvm.bsky.social">Bluesky</a>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Organizers</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      Lesley Lai [<a href="https://lesleylai.info/">Website</a>] [<a
        href="https://mastodon.gamedev.place/@lesley">Mastodon</a
      >] [<a href="https://codeberg.org/Lesley">Codeberg</a>]
    </li>
    <li>
      Charles Giessen [<a href="https://cdgiessen.github.io/">Website</a>]
    </li>
    <li>Jon Baker [<a href="https://jbaker.graphics/">Website</a>]</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="webring">
    <a href="https://graphics-programming.org/webring/frogs/gpvm/prev"> ⬅️ </a>
    <a href="https://graphics-programming.org/webring/" class="inline-wrapper">
      <span>GP Webring</span>
      <img
        src="https://graphics-programming.org/img/froge.webp"
        alt="a friendly froge"
      />
    </a>
    <a href="https://graphics-programming.org/webring/frogs/gpvm/next"> ➡️ </a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .webring {
    display: flex;
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    gap: var(--space-xxs);
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.9em;

    a {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--space-xxs);
    }

    img {
      display: inline;
      object-fit: contain;
      width: 1.5em;
      height: 1.5em;
    }
  }
</style>
